column5: Just got back from our annual moose trip with a few buddies, and had a great trip, we shot two Bull's and caught some nice walleye.
well those are some real nice 'eyes ya got there and a damn fine moose... if you dont mind me asking. where abouts were ya at?
Nice!  That thing is Huge, amazing that only a bullet or two will kill it.  Thanks for sharing, MTBF
Solid Trip...where abouts did you go?  My dad, bro and two uncles are up in 17 right now...i had to stay home
that's my kind of northern trip!  Great pics...they say it all
Great multi species report Court R It doesn't get any better than that!!! Great job you guys and thanks for sharing Leechman
WOW. Sounds like a great trip. nYOur going to be eating well for awhile. Thanks for sharing.
